        <h2>The MdS Personal Style Process</h2>
        <p>The MdS Personal Style Process includes three comprehensive phases that will help us connect you to your most authentic, powerful style. We honor the investment and vulnerability it takes to invite us into your views of self and style, and we strive to make the process transformative, fun, and safe.</p>

        
            
