    <div class="phases-wrapper">
            <div id="phase-1" class="phase-item">
                <div class="phase-headline">
                    <h3>Phase 1: Consultation + Style Discovery</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-text">
                    <p>Our most thorough and valuable part of the process. During this phase, we gather your inspirations, learn about your story and lifestyle, and develop your personalized Style Profile. We will teach you practical tools based on our discoveries so you can make confident choices with your style going forward.</p>
                    <p>We host this phase in a comfortable, well-appointed venue, allowing you to enjoy a sense of intentional relaxation, respite, and care.</p>
                    <p>We’ll use these findings to curate your personalized MdS Virtual Style Profile. Your Style Profile will be available on a password-protected client portal for you to continuously refer to and interact with, and includes your colors, body type, measurements, mood board, and shoppable links, all in one safe space.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-image">
                    <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/60944d7900683949d5bec241/1629999512754-RDLBSNUYQYWZBMMOF88H/%232-Phase-1_-Consultation-%2B-Style-Discovery.jpg?format=1000w" alt="" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="phase-2" class="phase-item">
                <div class="phase-headline">
                    <h3>Phase 2: Wardrobe Edit</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-text">
                    <p>During the Wardrobe Edit, we ensure that your current wardrobe reflects your style discovered in Phase 1. We assess what you currently own and how it can work with your personal style, creating outfit suggestions along the way.</p>
                    <p>We will also identify items in your wardrobe to eliminate, as well as any gaps to be filled. We’ll discuss an appropriate clothing budget, and help create a shopping list as you walk forward into your new image.</p>
                    <p>All notes, photos of outfit pairings, and shoppable links of suggested wardrobe additions will be uploaded to your Style Profile for you to refer back to.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-image">
                    <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/60944d7900683949d5bec241/1629999512692-NZGDBTXMN7LA4W299UU8/%233-Phase-2_-Wardrobe-Edit.jpg?format=1000w" alt="" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="phase-3" class="phase-item">
                <div class="phase-headline">
                    <h3>Phase 3: Shop + Fit</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-text">
                    <p>With every detail of your profile and personal style discoveries at hand, we shop for the most empowering clothing pieces for your life and your style.</p>
                    <p>We’ll bring the clothing to your home and incorporate these new pieces into your wardrobe. We will help create new outfit pairings using both new and existing wardrobe items, taking photos of each to upload to your Style Profile.</p>
                    <p>Should any of the new pieces require alterations, we will schedule those fittings until it’s just right. We will also complete any returns or exchanges.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-image">
                    <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/60944d7900683949d5bec241/1629999513207-OFNEA37N6ASOR03RA98M/%234-Phase-3_-Shop-%2B-Fit.jpg?format=1000w" alt="" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="phase-4" class="phase-item">
                <div class="phase-headline">
                    <h3>+ Beyond</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-text">
                    <p>Bypass any future stress surrounding style choices. If you have questions going forward (choosing an outfit for a special event, purchasing a new wardrobe item, or pairing shoes and accessories to an outfit) please consider us a go-to resource for real-time help! Call, text, or email. We are here to cheer you on!</p>
